{"id":60308,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/04/推特半月“三有”语录67条（15）-2/","date":"2010-04-18T10:00:06Z","modified":"2010-04-18T10:00:06Z","title":"推特半月“三有”语录67条（15）","content":"<div>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><strong>冉按：</strong>前几年我辑录了不少“大师们谈常识”来普及一些澄清迷雾的常识，以使被愚弄被颠倒的观念，得以传播。现在有了推特，就有了更多的传播渠道和辑录功能，因此诸位不妨把每半月的“三有”语录视为我辑录常识的延续。</span><span style=\"text-decoration:line-through\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2010</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">4</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">16</span></span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">6</span></span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">17</span></span><span>分于成都</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1</span></span><span>：<span>前年地震，温家宝说多难兴邦，大抵是夸地震来得好，应该多来点。今年西南大旱，他又说要痛定思痛，其曰痛在未兴修水利，无一语提及滥修水电站。国家已病入膏肓，温影帝却是个赤脚大仙。</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2</span></span></span><span><span>：有朋友说，不想当方丈的神父，不是好道长！我说，不想当演员的总理，不是好温家宝！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3</span></span></span><span><span>：晚间与山西对土改研究很深的作家鲁顺民兄吃饭，提及交城</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span></span></span><span><span>解放</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">”</span></span></span><span><span>时，宣传部叫老师要带领学生呼口号欢迎中共入城，老师不知喊什么口号，遂率学生齐呼：欢迎共匪！彼时哗然，今日桌上喷饭。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">4</span></span></span><span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/lingcangzhou\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">lingcangzhou</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">: </span></span></span><span><span>《南平血案校门前纪念花墙及横幅被强拆》该官员立即回应：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span></span></span><span><span>全南平的记者都归我管，都必须给我看记者证</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">!”</span></span></span><span><span>并威胁羊城晚报记者：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span></span></span><span><span>你在这里煽动和挑拨群众。你等着，我有办法收拾你</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">!”</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">5</span></span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">  RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/wumaohua\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">wumaohua</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">: </span></span><span>南京著名杂文家吴</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">×</span></span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1996</span></span><span>年在上海，吴祖光亲口对我说：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span></span><span>你知道我为什么看不起吴欢？尽他妈的跟一伙权贵子弟混在一起！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">”</span></span><span>我当时没想到他会骂自己的儿子，而且当着我这个晚辈。那天吃中饭的就我和他两个人，连个转弯的话题也没有。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">6</span></span><span>：</span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/newsinchina\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">newsinchina</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">: </span></span></span><span><span>熊猫们如果不嫌烦</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span></span></span><span><span>我建议你们动作更大一些</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span></span></span><span><span>也不用这么客气</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">.</span></span></span><span><span>直接上传唤证没收电脑最好再关那些不老实的家伙几天</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">.</span></span></span><span><span>不过相信我</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span></span></span><span><span>当他们被释放出来时基本上一个钢铁战士就练成了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span></span></span><span><span>你们丫的就真正制造出敌人来了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">!</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">7</span></span></span><span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/mynamexu\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">mynamexu</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">: </span></span></span><span><span>美国一位将军曾经笑曰：你们中国的大炮是不会袭击美国滴，因为中国管大炮发射的司令长官的儿子就住在我们的旧金山。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">8</span></span></span><span><span>：有了中国政府，世界上都不存在黑社会了。不是中国政府消灭了黑社会，而是世界上再强悍的黑社会，都只不过是对他们的蹩脚模仿罢了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">9</span></span></span><span><span>：在这危机的时刻，请你们保护自己的灵魂，你们必须相信，这个谎言和暴力的时代会崩溃。道德意识无论如何是不能忘记的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">——</span></span></span><span><span>捷克剧作家恰彼克</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">10</span></span></span><span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/darkloli\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">darkloli</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> #2015 </span></span></span><span><span>年冬天，我去排队领做爱券，漫长的队伍里大包小包塞得满满，还有人准备了帐篷。背靠贴着</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span></span></span><span><span>绿霸娘需要你</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">”</span></span></span><span><span>宣传画的墙壁，和几个人谈笑风生</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span></span></span><span><span>你说领导用不用领做爱券</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span></span></span><span><span>我当了领导，第一件事儿就是向秘书要一打做爱券，只看不做</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">”“</span></span></span><span><span>看着看着忽然高潮</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">”</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">11</span></span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">  </span></span><span>你对有些人说某某上台，不一定比现在的领导人更好，怎么看？老实说，这样的思维很没质量。要紧的不是在没有实现自由选举前抽象地比准好谁烂，而在于有良好的机制保障你的选择自由：即选错了，你还有机会用较小的代价和平自由地选你心中所选。</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/search?q=%23randa\" title=\"#randa\">#randa</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">12</span></span><span>：</span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/jauyiu\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">jauyiu</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">: </span></span></span><span><span>班里有个女生，色狼一个，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">QQ</span></span></span><span><span>昵称叫</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span></span></span><span><span>拒绝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">”</span></span></span><span><span>，于是我好奇地问了句：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span></span></span><span><span>你为啥叫这个名字啊？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">”</span></span></span><span><span>她回过来一个羞涩表情说：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span></span></span><span><span>难道你不觉得加上偏旁比较含蓄吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">*^_^*”</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">13</span></span></span><span><span>：据计生委说，从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2001—2006</span></span></span><span><span>年，中国出生的有生理缺陷的婴儿数量增加了近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">50%</span></span></span><span><span>。再加上毒奶粉、毒疫苗、黑煤窑、血铅超标、让领导先走、愚民教育，可以大规模地降低儿童成长为正常人的概率，极权统治由此万世可期也。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">14</span></span></span><span><span>：读毕杜导正的《赵紫阳还说过什么？》最强烈的感受是，在极权制度下，一：高官们也非常恐惧，二：对于政策的制定，他们也只是谈言微中的射覆者。除所得之好处外，他们也颇类不明真相的股栗群众。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">15</span></span></span><span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">@</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/tengbiao\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">tengbiao</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span></span></span><span><span>受迫害幻想狂和斯德歌尔摩综合症是一枚硬币的两面，是极权下的孪生兄弟，二者互相作用。常做动机揣测、强迫别人对某事表态，都是对自己及所做的事不够自信，不是真正理性的个人主义者。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">16</span></span></span><span><span>：我一直认为只要一个人有做人的底线和相对真诚，左倾和激进的陈独秀，依然值得温和改良的胡适去监狱里看望和营救。这叫道不同亦相为谋。表达乃至坚持自己的观念固然重要，但拥有一点毋固毋必的心态不是毫无意义。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">17</span></span></span><span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/liudimouse\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman;color:#800080\">liudimouse</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">: </span></span></span><span><span>原来一个老师上课讲的笑话说是他家楼下有个棺材铺，每天都放同一首歌，有一次他忍不住了进去问老板：你们这是什么歌啊？老板说：张学友的，总有一天等到你</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">…..</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">18</span></span></span><span><span>：上海买菜刀、火车票、重庆网络等实名制，睢宁良民证，整个中国全面把民众裸体化管理。而官员财产、政务公开、财务透明等则全部大张旗鼓地暗箱操作。两相对比，你就可以看出一个荒谬无比的政府。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">19</span></span></span><span><span>：政府权力边界过大的同时，必然把所有社会矛盾和冲突都包揽到自己身上。政府就会成为社会矛盾和冲突的当事方，难于做到应有的超然中立，难于平衡利益格局，这对政府公信</span></span><span>力无疑是莫大的伤害。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">——</span></span><span>杜导正</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">20</span></span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span></span><span>去年山西政府搞煤矿的国进民退时说是为了安全，今天的王家岭矿难受困</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">153</span></span><span>人，是对他们撒谎的最好回答。六十年来政府抢劫民众财产是一惯的，再富裕粗豪的煤老板也只好打掉牙齿往肚里吞。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">21</span></span><span>：<span>独裁政府当然不管孩子的死活，但为人父母却必须为孩子的健康而抗争。孩子致残致死不敢反抗的父母是孬种，中国的孬种父母何其多也。不知这些人听周云蓬兄的</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span></span></span><span><span>中国孩子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">”</span></span></span><span><span>会不会有点惭愧？</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/search?q=%23zhaolianhai\" title=\"#zhaolianhai\">#zhaolianhai</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">22</span></span></span><span><span>：有许多人不为权利和自由而战，其借口是家有孩子。但当他的孩子受害的时候，他还是不敢为孩子讨说法。如此双重怯懦的民众，自由哪里会眷顾你？</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/search?q=%23zhaolianhai\" title=\"#zhaolianhai\">#zhaolianhai</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">23</span></span></span><span><span>：生在这个独裁国家，我觉得你许多事忍气吞声，都可以理解。惟独对孩子惨死致残默不作声的父母，我觉得不可理喻。自然对任何阻扰为孩子维权的恶行，都令人义愤填膺。</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/search?q=%23zhaolianhai\" title=\"#zhaolianhai\">#zhaolianhai</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">24</span></span></span><span><span>：中国民众必须知道一个残酷的事实：如果你不想让你的孩子成为奴隶主的添头，在中国生小孩是需要勇气的。如若没有替孩子的自由和权利而战的准备就最好别生。</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/search?q=%23zhaolianhai\" title=\"#zhaolianhai\">#zhaolianhai</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">25</span></span></span><span><span>：免仔被害、护犊之情，是动物本能。许多中国父母已经被独裁政府阉割掉仅有的一点反抗本能。连这样的本能都没有了，做人还有什么意思？</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/search?q=%23zhaolianhai\" title=\"#zhaolianhai\">#zhaolianhai</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">26</span></span></span><span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/yimaobuba\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">yimaobuba</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span></span></span><span><span>去年十月我在希腊雅典的宪法广场边上的一家酒店露台上吃饭欣赏卫城夜景时，一个老美要死不死的跑来说：你是中国人吗？你们的国庆阅兵很壮观。我气不打一处来的破口大骂：独裁者强征了老子的税款，然后炫耀武力吓唬我们有啥好看。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">27</span></span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/wangxy1\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">wangxy1</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">: RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/xiaoyong8964\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">xiaoyong8964</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">: 60</span></span><span>大月饼，我问一朋友：你怎么看月饼？朋友悠然：猪看到屠夫磨刀，有什么值得兴奋的？</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">28</span></span><span>：</span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HeQinglian\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">HeQinglian</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">: </span></span></span><span><span>英国的《金融时报》报道：</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span></span><span><span>世界近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">200</span></span></span><span><span>个政府中有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">18</span></span></span><span><span>个对互联网实行政治性的控制：分三个档次：彻底过滤，如中国，越南和伊朗；实质性地过滤，如利比亚，埃塞俄比亚和沙特阿拉伯；选择性过滤，如巴基斯坦，泰国和阿塞拜疆。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">29</span></span></span><span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/trotrotro\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">trotrotro</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span></span></span><span><span>我党最伟大的地方，就在于能够一次又一次战胜陈独秀、李立三、王明、博古、彭德怀、刘少奇、四人帮、胡耀邦、赵紫阳、上海帮这些反党分子和他们的反党集团</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">30</span></span></span><span><span>：感谢这位朋友的好联。谭判五年，故改。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/feifei7295\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">feifei7295</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span></span></span><span><span>谭今慨古，为校园冤魂舍身者其谁？系狱五载，义重古蜀三千里，而今从头学作人；赵杰吴豪，给结石宝贝请命者有几？蒙冤三月，情撼华夏九州同，自古父爱山连海。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">31</span></span></span><span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/pufei\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">pufei</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">: </span></span></span><span><span>报告有司：田原那句中国人的事情要靠中国人自己，我认为暗含讽刺中央领导人中有多位外国人父母这一事实，是典型的指桑骂槐，煽动颠覆国家政权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">32</span></span></span><span><span>：慕容雪村：他拿着枪，你买把水果刀就算凶器；他日夜宣淫，你下载个黄片就算流氓；他大发横财，你摆个摊就算违法；他住高楼别墅，你搭个窝棚还要被强拆；我在想，他这么牛逼，为什么还如此恐惧？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">33</span></span></span><span><span>：如果国家有着无法挑战的绝对权威，那是不利于公民社会的建立的。当国家的利益取代公民的利益，那么国家无非成了剥夺公民利益的工具。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">—</span></span></span><span><span>王笛《茶馆：成都的公共生活和微观世界》</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">P4</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">34</span></span><span>：主席忙出访、贪官忙三讲、工人忙下岗、农民忙上访、学生忙上网、法轮功忙反党。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">——</span></span><span>北京大学学生顺口溜</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">35</span></span><span>：</span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/liuyun1989\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">liuyun1989</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">: @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/ranyunfei\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman;color:#800080\">ranyunfei</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span></span></span><span><span>中央忙搭幫、地方忙拆房、高官忙分贓、小吏忙嫖娼、五毛忙請賞、推友忙翻墻、有司忙猖狂、屁民忙罵娘、兲朝忙死亡。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">36</span></span></span><span><span>：我无甚一劳永逸的良药，助你成长。我只有非常平实的话告知你：努力生存、努力上进、努力做自己想做的事、把自己锻炼成器，而不是一心想去影响他人。多从自己能做之事做起，而不要想什么大事。于社会和自己有寸进，且能坚持，即善莫大焉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">—</span></span></span><span><span>答杨君</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">37</span></span></span><span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/zhangming1\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">zhangming1</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">: </span></span></span><span><span>铁凝说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span></span></span><span><span>作协有一万个存在的理由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">.</span></span></span><span><span>我说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span></span></span><span><span>做爱协会有一万个存在理由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span></span></span><span><span>作家协会一个都没有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">.</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">38</span></span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/bxxg\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">bxxg</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New 