pan style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">4</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">14</span></span><span>日</span><span>零时起将汽、柴油价格每吨均提高</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">320</span></span></span><span><span>元．各地民众获得消息后纷纷表示，由于涨价油品并不包括地沟油，所以对实际生活影响并不大．</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">61</span></span></span><span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/blogtd\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman;color:#800080\">blogtd</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">: #</span></span></span><span><span>乖闻乱播</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span></span><span><span>据最新出土的秦代官方文献研究表明，秦代煤矿事故根据造成的人员伤亡，分为四个等级，分别是：特别重大事故　重大事故　较大事故和一般事故．而根据救援的难度和感动的人数，又分为四个级别，分别是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">:</span></span></span><span><span>特别伟大奇迹，伟大奇迹，较大奇迹和一般奇迹．</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">62</span></span></span><span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/blogtd\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman;color:#800080\">blogtd</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">: </span></span></span><span><span>據最新考古研究發現，秦朝的媒礦對礦工生命毫不在乎，導致礦難事故頻繁，為防死難礦工鬧事，朝廷派出大量維穩人員下井長期駐守，以保證煤礦生產照常進行．這些維穩人員就是今天大家看到秦朝兵馬俑．</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">63</span></span></span><span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">RT @</span><a href=\"http://twitter.com/shijinxia\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">shijinxia</span></a><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">: </span></span></span><span><span>力所能及的慈善，不光是为了让这个世界更加有希望，也是为了减轻你自己的罪恶，这个事情和政府无关，但是和社会有关</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">——</span></span></span><span><span>韩寒</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">64</span></span></span><span><span>：美国人不需要像韩寒那样转弯抹角的说话方式。他们有要说的话，完全可以直截了当地说出来，韩寒运用的是一种对美国人非常陌生，也不需要的说话方式。其次，像韩寒那样拐着弯，费劲地说话，难以设想在美国会有像在中国这么众多、这么热烈的听众。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">—</span></span></span><span><span>徐贲《美国人读不懂韩寒》</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">65</span></span></span><span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">twitter</span></span></span><span><span>上的消息，当然应该证实。但说不应把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">twitter</span></span></span><span><span>当成消息源，就不一定对。推特的自我纠错和质疑功能的快捷性，传播力量和准确性，恐怕不输于被管制得一塌糊涂任何中国传统传媒。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">66</span></span></span><span><span>：从当局设置关卡不让记者进灾区、拒绝外国救援来看，除了在他们看来玉树属藏区的特殊性外，当局对于地震灾难救援吸取的教训是越封锁、越自闭越好。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">67</span></span></span><span><span>：灾难一经发生，官方不是把主要精力放在救灾上，而是一惯地封锁消息，以掩盖被天灾逼出来的人祸大灾难。林昭几十年前就说，中国的报纸是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span></span></span><span><span>整套特务恐怖统治机构的组成部分</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">”</span></span></span><span><span>，信然。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n</div>\n<div>© 日拱一卒，不期速成。非商业性转载，请全文转载并署作者名。商业性使用，请联系作者。欢迎访问我的独立微博客<a href=\"http://ranyunfei.shoutem.com\">http://ranyunfei.shoutem.com</a>和推特：<a href=\"http://twitter.com/ranyunfei\">http://twitter.com/ranyunfei</a></div>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[18328,171,8339,8635,18856,19381,11248,8710,10605,9540,9000,10782,8872,10228,12031,8604,15020,14202,15515,9553,9475,17580,9715,9105,14460,8614]}